Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位於橫川·輕井澤之間的碓冰嶺是國鐵最險的路段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初修鐵路的時候用的是阿伯特齒軌式鐵軌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在兩軌正中間加上一條鋸齒狀的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓機車的齒輪咬合於上  用以爬坡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只有舊線路留著這種軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提  這裡的最大坡度可達千分之66.7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的是每走1000米  高度就會上升66米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉  才不是這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對鐵路而言是極陡的坡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天作為特別培訓  要讓你們駕駛這輛輔助機車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早點搞定早吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別掃興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是ED42嗎  我還以為要開EF63
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡這麼老的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪敢哪敢  十分榮幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急行「白山」號是由車頭3台ED42型電力機車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間夾著8節客車  加上車尾的1台組成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我繃緊神經  好好駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  現在來決定由誰坐在車尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  尾部機車可是最難控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不事先商量好時間安排和警笛信號的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就盡力別拖後腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛座果然很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在這裡展現我的駕駛才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下來是下坡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  那個亂七八糟的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧  櫻井那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛是要把主幹控制器歸零的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？速度在變快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須使用電制動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我不知道怎麼操作制動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看說明書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小海  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵的尾部機車好像在推著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我給她發下信號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井那傢伙在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  快進行制動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你那邊在磨磨蹭蹭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去速度只會不斷變快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況下繼續制動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間的車廂會被擠歪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會脫線的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君  速度升得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  正在想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  速度是不是在變快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話  會出大事故的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣  只能賭一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是國鐵引以為傲的模擬訓練程序  做的不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來  好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為公安隊…不  作為國鐵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們全都忘記了最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個事故是由你們全員造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是不太適合公安隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,況且  還是代理班長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就快下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我抽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  又抽到烏龜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  輪到高山君你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說有話說  是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安隊的制服  我倒覺得挺合適你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  現在在我面前的高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子有點不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得高山君只要相信自己就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警四的成員人都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛成田先生來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明天的實習先不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為依照現在的情況也出不了什麼成績
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天大家一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為放鬆精神去逛街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得來輕井澤一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  也叫上岩泉君和小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邀請櫻井的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是代理班長的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（明天，我們要去輕井澤街上走走，櫻井也一起來吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為聽說全是實習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒帶什麼過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是匆忙買的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  很適合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  岩泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全找不到好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是只知道吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是接受義大利菜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有個很好的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  就那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我就沒有什麼要說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道無論札沼穿什麼都很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是什麼誇獎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  櫻井呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願能早點和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  警四打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假期很愉快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打斷你們的休假不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有件事情要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望高山君能去迎接一個重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方似乎指名一定要高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  去紀念禮拜堂就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是被拜託了一點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完事了就去找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井可能不久就到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是聯絡我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓她去你們那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就回來  待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（我剛到輕井澤）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  我沒問小海他們的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  沒有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙他們沒和你一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到櫻井也會穿這種衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎  我又不是討厭這種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  為什麼特意來教會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底準備幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  那個  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本是想能在工作上幫幫忙才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在這種沒人的教會與小葵見面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  還撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我萬萬沒想到會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒謊是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  必須要說明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃亞？
